issue.title: Ign Fuel Upload - Got "Core dumped" for some Models
Ign Fuel Upload - Got "Core dumped" for some Models

content.raw:
Would you be able to get a backtrace? You can start gdb like:

~~~
gdb --args ruby `which ign` fuel upload ...
~~~

Then inside gdb `r` to run, and `bt` to get the backtrace after the crash.
content.html:

Fix: #!/ignitionrobotics/ign-msgs/pull-requests/172

The listed models have empty `<description>` tags.
